Threat-IP data (optional, bundled at build time via
scripts/build-threatlist.sh) is derived from IPsum
(https://github.com/stamparm/ipsum), released into the public domain under
the Unlicense. IPsum aggregates publicly available blocklists; MatrixNet
uses level 3 (addresses present on three or more independent lists). The
list is advisory only — MatrixNet labels matching remote addresses and
never blocks traffic.
